1
00:00:01,562 --> 00:00:09,695
This is Radeon Voice Skill Foundry running as a public full-stack product, not a static mockup.

2
00:00:09,695 --> 00:00:13,762
The cinematic cover is hosted on Cloudflare Pages.

3
00:00:13,762 --> 00:00:23,420
Every API action is forwarded through an authenticated same-origin gateway to an AMD Radeon Pro W7900 running ROCm 7.2.1.

4
00:00:23,420 --> 00:00:32,570
The product turns a private spoken procedure into a governed, reusable Agent Skill before risky actions are allowed.

5
00:00:35,071 --> 00:00:43,885
I open the Voice module and upload the same twenty-point-three-nine second Chinese procedure used in the Radeon validation.

6
00:00:43,885 --> 00:00:48,292
Qwen three A-S-R transcribes the audio on the W7900.

7
00:00:48,292 --> 00:00:57,596
Voice Evidence version zero point three measures source integrity, level, clipping, silence, signal-to-noise ratio, dropout, and multi-frame burst loss.

8
00:00:57,596 --> 00:01:07,879
This recording passes at one hundred out of one hundred, and the server binds the original transcript hash to the skill.

9
00:01:10,383 --> 00:01:14,209
Now the Radeon model adapter compiles the spoken procedure.

10
00:01:14,209 --> 00:01:21,012
Qwen three, four-B Instruct combines the transcript, the aligned action trace, and retrieved local policy evidence.

11
00:01:21,012 --> 00:01:29,514
This is a real model call, so the interface keeps the compiling state visible while the W7900 generates structured output.

12
00:01:29,514 --> 00:01:37,167
During this live generation window, the public interface does not substitute a cached policy or accelerate the footage.

13
00:01:37,167 --> 00:01:43,969
It waits for the Radeon response and preserves the measured latency as part of the evidence.

14
00:01:43,969 --> 00:01:52,047
The runtime then merges deterministic safety guardrails ahead of the model result and advances directly into the Policy module.

15
00:01:54,386 --> 00:01:58,199
The policy makes the hidden intent executable.

16
00:01:58,199 --> 00:02:06,368
The Chinese instruction not to send automatically becomes a must-not rule and `mail.send` is denied.

17
00:02:06,368 --> 00:02:09,636
Salary data becomes a redaction rule.

18
00:02:09,636 --> 00:02:12,359
Missing ownership opens human review.

19
00:02:12,359 --> 00:02:16,716
Calendar holds remain conditional on a due date.

20
00:02:16,716 --> 00:02:28,154
Seven generated tests cover voice integrity, the happy path, automatic sending, sensitive data, missing context, conditional scope, and unapproved network writes.

21
00:02:30,657 --> 00:02:34,656
Verification executes those unsafe paths before promotion.

22
00:02:34,656 --> 00:02:41,511
The server resolves the authoritative compile run instead of trusting client-side permissions.

23
00:02:41,511 --> 00:02:43,796
All seven fixtures pass.

24
00:02:43,796 --> 00:02:56,365
Automatic email sending is blocked before tool execution, sensitive data is removed, and four governance receipts record the review and block decisions.

25
00:02:56,365 --> 00:03:05,505
The Proof module exposes the measured Radeon runtime, the generated skill, and a downloadable hash-bound package.

26
00:03:08,008 --> 00:03:12,607
The verified result is saved into local procedural memory.

27
00:03:12,607 --> 00:03:20,783
I immediately reuse the same skill without asking the model to regenerate its rules and tests.

28
00:03:20,783 --> 00:03:29,469
Compatibility remains bound to the current runtime, verifier, tool contract, policy, skill definition, and Voice Evidence schema.

29
00:03:29,469 --> 00:03:36,112
This is reusable proof, not just a transcript or a one-time workflow recording.

30
00:03:38,622 --> 00:03:44,001
The same W7900 produced the optimization evidence used by the submission.

31
00:03:44,001 --> 00:03:57,204
At concurrency eight, vLLM graph serving reached two hundred fifty-seven point six five aggregate output tokens per second, twelve point four seven times the serialized Transformers path.

32
00:03:57,204 --> 00:04:08,940
Native Qwen three A-S-R batching reached eighty-five point three five times aggregate real-time and was six point six six times faster than sequential inference.

33
00:04:08,940 --> 00:04:13,830
The current regression suite passes thirty-five out of thirty-five tests.

34
00:04:16,355 --> 00:04:33,248
The complete path is now public: Cloudflare, authenticated gateway, W7900 speech recognition, local policy retrieval, Radeon model compilation, least-privilege enforcement, adversarial proof, and procedural memory.

35
00:04:33,248 --> 00:04:35,951
Actions capture what happened.

36
00:04:35,951 --> 00:04:42,709
Voice captures why, when, exceptions, and what must never happen.

37
00:04:42,709 --> 00:04:44,736
Speak the S-O-P.

38
00:04:44,736 --> 00:04:46,763
Prove the Skill.
